[[title|Migration]]

<p><b>Warning!</b> Running migrations can cause loss of data. Please use only as directed by 
your system administrator or software maintenance provider.</p> 

<p>Migrations update the structure of the underlying system database. When system 
updates occur there may be necessary database changes. These changes will be conducted 
by your system administrator or software maintenance provider. The migrations module provides tools for maintaining 
the state of the database for these changes.</p>
